dct_description_sm: compiled and drawn in the Cartographic Section of the National Geographic Society ; executed by Albert H. Bumstead and James M. Darley.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
Includes insets of Byrd's South Pole flight, Antarctic Archipelago and King Edward VII Land.
